f: aSelector meta: isMeta 	"Any change to an additionsToViewer... method can invalidate existing etoy vocabularies.	The #respondsTo: test is to allow loading the FlexibleVocabularies change set without having to worry about method ordering."	"do nothing because this is just the preload."	super noteCompilationOf: aSelector meta: isMeta! !!StandardScriptingSystem class methodsFor: '*flexiblevocabularies-scripting' stamp: 'nk 10/11/2003 17:48'!noteCompilationOf: aSelector meta: isMeta 	"Any change to an additionsToViewer... method can invalidate existing etoy vocabularies.	The #respondsTo: test is to allow loading the FlexibleVocabularies change set without having to worry about method ordering."	"do nothing because this is just the preload."	super noteCompilationOf: aSelector meta: isMeta! !